Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years have passed\Nsince the Paramount War at Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew\Neach completed individual training,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and in order to move on\Nto the next stage, the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they return to Sabaody Archipelago!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? None of the others are here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Take another good look at the poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bounty has to be\Nat least seventy million berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not accepting any captains below that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only tell you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not good enough for me.\NI'm not gonna drink with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure-Kill Green Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, girl.\NWill you drink with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.19,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm all bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:05.86,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The manly Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,has returned from hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook's concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates wanted for the Straw Hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have kept you waiting, Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll set sail soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did it hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
