Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see Sabaody Archipelago there in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, this is as far as we can take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No one must find out about our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need that! That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never know what might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you hide your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, everyone thinks you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to what happened two years ago,\Nthe whole world knows your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're discovered,\Nyou might never make it off these islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've loaded your pack with\N500 changes of clothes, 1,000 lunches,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and a five-year supply\Nof handkerchiefs, tissues, and towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also a three-year supply\Nof drinking water and snacks... and silver cutlery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And a three-year supply of toothbrushes, soap, hand lotion and bug bite ointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.73,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,You overdid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you can safely meet up with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thanks for everything, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:37.15,Default,Sweetpea,0,0,0,,I hear Sabaody has become less safe these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:42.89,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,Indeed. That's why the Navy\Nhas been keeping a close eye on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.96,Default,Sweetpea,0,0,0,,Please be extra careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever need us, the Kuja Pirates will always come to your aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And... I have one more request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that... Go, but please don't say "goodbye."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I never say goodbye to nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I always plan to see them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.76,Alt,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wants to see me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what they call...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a proposal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.84,Default,Gloriosa,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hancock told me so many times to be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You bumped into me on purpose, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's in serious trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:55.59,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Grove #13\NShakky's Rip-Off Bar
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.05,0:07:55.59,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}Grove #13\NShakky's Rip-Off Bar
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.26,DefaultLow2,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.59,DefaultLow2,,0,0,0,,The first one here was that idiot swordsman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I forsee a difficult voyage ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The second one here was Franky-chan.\NHe came about ten days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and went straight to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Sunny is safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a scratch on her.\NI finished coating her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And this guy did a great job as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Call it a badge of honor!\NI regret nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! A year to recover!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:21.59,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yes! A year to recover!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize you had such a strong sense of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We owe you big time, Duval.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? I'm handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to pay you back, young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Through rain and shine, storm and snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood my ground and protected the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,from those bloodthirsty pirates!\NDay after day after day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hurting all over, but I kept on fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Duval-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, how'd you get hurt this badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, fall for me...\NI mean, listen to me, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, even the Navy showed up—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.75,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And Nami-chan showed up third.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-swan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?! Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She got bored and went\Nto town to do some shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What about my epic struggle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san's shopping! Nami-san's shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp-chan arrived fourth.\NHe got here three days ago and went to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper-chan was fifth.\NHe arrived yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Brook-chan came to the island for his concert today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, counting you, there are already seven of you on the archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin and Luffy are the only ones left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no easy feat just getting to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are an amazing bunch of pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you might all make it back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't know you were the one training Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be unbelievably strong by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him for about six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see how he's grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Grown, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't wait to see how much Nami-san's grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Young master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I endured two years of arduous training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to show off the results.\NSo I gotta shake off any signs of temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:24.67,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Grove #47
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.71,0:10:24.67,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}Grove #47
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Some rookies are fighting again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the pirates would settle down\Nafter Whitebeard's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the exact opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates have been coming from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole island is pretty much\Npart of the Lawless Lands now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackbeard, Kid, and Drake\Nare doing as they please in the New World
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're the ones who'll follow—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Surpass them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rumors are true after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,People thought they died fighting the Navy here on Sabaody Archipelago two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But they really did come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it.\NThe most powerful crew on the island right now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is it Nami?! Maybe Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Pirate Hunter" Zoro.\NHe's got a bounty of 120 million berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Black Leg" Sanji.\NHis bounty's 77 million berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She became a wanted criminal at the age of eight. Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Her bounty's 80 million berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And the "Cotton Candy Lover"—\NTony Tony Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With a 50-berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so low!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:59.00,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}"Straw Hat Pirates"\NZoro, Sanji, Robin, Chopper
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.90,0:11:59.00,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}"Straw Hat Pirates"\NZoro, Sanji, Robin, Chopper
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Luffy there, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! Please get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally some worthy opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you stopping us, Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If we pick a fight with them,\NStraw Hat Luffy won't keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a good idea to get into unnecessary conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,when we're about to enter the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that talking raccoon dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Raccoon dogs can't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you got here first, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't believe you didn't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So Sanji and Robin finally made it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Never seen anything\Nlike that before, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds exhausting.\NLet's just ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The target, Nico Robin, is a Devil Fruit user.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in trouble if she fights back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to catch her off guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They might all be here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want Nami-san and Robin-chan\Nto get a taste of my improved cooking immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, I better go see\Nif the kitchen on the Sunny is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll go shopping for ingredients!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bump into me knowing who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see?\NHow you made me look like a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You humiliated me in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, an elite pirate with a bounty of 400 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down on your knees, fear me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and beg for your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he value his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he finally realized\Nwhat a huge mistake he made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And now he can't even speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's that scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute ago, a man with a long nose and a woman with long hair embarrassed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Captain's in a bad mood right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You better apologize, and quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,On your knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One wrong move now and you'll be crow food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Our captain is quick to pull the trigger, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on the ground already!\NThat's Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to die?!\NApologize already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.66,Alt,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did he do something just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hancock was right.\NGuess I better put it on after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zoro! Sanji! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you guys?\NI haven't seen you in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought Zoro and Sanji\Nwould get to be so chummy in just two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are you guys ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's still following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys feeling shy, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That raccoon dog seems to know an awful lot\Nabout us Straw Hats, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about that too.\NYou don't think... Have a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Cotton Candy Lover, Chopper,\Nworth 50 berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew's pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys seem a little different!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew must've dumped him on this island when they were still alive and now he's gone feral.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks we're his masters.\NThat's why he's following us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's ditch the fox and keep the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If our pet's the one on the wanted poster,\Nwe'll look more convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna keep it? What does it eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cotton candy, what else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't have any!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need you anymore! Just get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a cucumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary! Robin, that's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Hey, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They took Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, shouldn't we tell Captain Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You've already met Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have new members by now, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we better rescue Robin as quickly as possible, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting from Sabaody Archipelago!\NWe've captured Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And we also captured... a fox?\NIt bit her and won't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky's all fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I don't have to worry about the Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Viva Sabaody!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I gotta focus on cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to stock up on the best ingredients I can find first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I need ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll whip up something so good\Nit'll knock Nami-san and Robin-chan off their feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,this place doesn't have anything interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you might want to check out the shop\Non the coastline of Grove #42.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you! 'Preciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, fisherman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you sell me something cheap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nobody home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you the owner of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The green-haired guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Green hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible! You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:09.66,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Old man, I wanna fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:15.36,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Young man, you don't look like\Na fishing type of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:18.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,,I promised to meet up\Nwith my friends on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:22.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,But I arrived first,\Nnone of the others are here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:25.88,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Since I'm first,\NI have nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Can you take me out to sea on your fishing boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:31.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll take you with me on that boat right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:32.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Get on board and wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...that's what I told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He had green hair and three swords?\NWas he wearing a sash?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And a big scar on his eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A scar on his eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him! That's the guy!\NAre you his friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... we're acquainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him to get on my fishing boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.88,Flashback,,0,0,0,,No, young man, not that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,That's a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:12.46,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Men! It's time to set sail for the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:14.36,Flashback,,0,0,0,,The place of our dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:18.09,Flashback,,0,0,0,,W-Wake up, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:20.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,You're on the wrong ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...so, he's probably on his way to Fishman Island by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange that he'd get here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've known he'd get into trouble right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't that easy to kill.\NAt least I can tell the others what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway you got any fish for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:21:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish? You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look in the water!\NSomething's surfacing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.59,0:22:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a galleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it break under the water pressure\Nbecause of a bad coating job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.80,0:22:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did a Sea King hit it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it was sliced in two by a blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.34,0:22:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How could anyone do something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,ruined our dreams for the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.95,0:22:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fate's a fickle thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You should blame your own destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It brough a curse upon your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullcrap, you're the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's on top of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:22:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.61,0:23:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I got on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the wrong ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One by one, the Straw Hats are gathering on the Sunny, preparing to set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.66,0:23:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Navy catches wind of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and sets out for Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The opponent that cornered Luffy & Co. two years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.36,0:23:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,sets their sights on the crew once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.23,0:23:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Navy Has Set Out\NThe Straw Hats in Danger"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
